CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 12, 1956, pg. A21, reads: "'The Simple Things' ... of life, sings Jeri Jackson, Carnegie Tech student (Pittsburgh) during the Scotch 'n' Soda show, 'Head Over Heels.' With Jeri are Ron Fritts, Ralph Downey, Al Gorelick and Francis Luzzatto.  Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Ron Fritts, Ralph Downey, Al Gorelick, and Francis Luzzatto, lifting singer Jeri Jackson, performing during the Scotch 'n' Soda show at Carnegie Tech
